{"type": "article", "id": 26, "title": "当水果遇上磁共振", "description": "当水果遇上磁共振", "date": "2014-04-28T20:30:56Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [{"id": 92, "name": "水果"}, {"id": 93, "name": "核磁共振"}], "category": 12, "column": null, "author": 2, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 22, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160604214304nLlYD3UJiHIwOMjx.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"vertical-align:baseline;text-align:justify;\">\r\n\t医院常用磁共振成像（MRI）拍摄人体内部情况，检查脑部、心血管、关节等部位的病变。如果把水果放进核磁共振机会看到什么呢？\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"vertical-align:baseline;\">\r\n\t波士顿大学医学院的一位核磁共振技师 Andy Ellison 最近就在做这事。Ellison将凤梨、香蕉、西瓜、玉米等蔬菜和水果放进一台科研用的飞利浦 3 Tesla 核磁共振机，结果相当漂亮，<a href=\"http://petapixel.com/2012/10/18/beautiful-animations-showing-mri-scans-of-fruits-and-vegetables/\" target=\"_blank\">这里</a>你可以看到更多：\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align:center;vertical-align:baseline;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"http://121.201.7.32:8001/uploads/image/201404/8cd172e877b1.gif\" alt=\"\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align:center;vertical-align:baseline;\">\r\n\t草莓\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align:center;vertical-align:baseline;\">\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align:center;vertical-align:baseline;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"http://121.201.7.32:8001/uploads/image/201404/331f7034e8e7.gif\" alt=\"\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align:center;vertical-align:baseline;\">\r\n\t番茄\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align:center;vertical-align:baseline;\">\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align:center;vertical-align:baseline;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"http://121.201.7.32:8001/uploads/image/201404/542903b60a58.gif\" alt=\"\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align:center;vertical-align:baseline;\">\r\n\t西瓜\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align:center;vertical-align:baseline;\">\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align:center;vertical-align:baseline;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"http://121.201.7.32:8001/uploads/image/201404/17b436177bfd.gif\" alt=\"\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align:center;vertical-align:baseline;\">\r\n\t香蕉\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align:center;vertical-align:baseline;\">\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}